c
f'(c) = \lim \limits_{x \to c}\frac{f(x) - f(c)}{x - c}.
\lim \limits_{x\to c}(f(x) - f(c)) = \lim_{x \to c}\frac{f(x) - f(c)}{x - c}(x-c) = f'(c)\cdot 0 = 0.
